  <h2>Strawberry shortcake is one of my favorite desserts!</h2>
  <p>Little round shortcakes with strawberry gel, strawberries, whipped cream, and sugar.</p>

  <h3>Ingredients</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Shortcake</li>
    <li>Strawberry gel</li>
    <li>Chopped strawberries</li>
    <li>Whipped cream</li>
    <li>Sugar</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Steps</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Chop strawberries</li>
    <li>Place strawberries, gel, and teaspoon of sugar into a bowl</li>
    <li>Mix well</li>
    <li>Place shortcake onto plate and top with strawberry mixture</li>
    <li>Top with whipped cream</li>
    <li>Pour a glass of milk or favorite beverage</li>
    <li>Enjoy</li>
  </ol>

